import React from 'react'
import {
    Menu,
    MenuButton,
    MenuList,
    MenuItem,
    MenuItemOption,
    MenuGroup,
    MenuOptionGroup,
    MenuDivider,
  } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function ProfileDropdown({target}) {
  return (
    <Menu >
    <MenuButton >
      {target}
    </MenuButton>
    <MenuList mr='14' px='4' py='6' border='none' shadow='lg' rounded='2xl'>
      <MenuItem>Download</MenuItem>
    </MenuList>
  </Menu>
  )
}

export default ProfileDropdown
